title: About Me
text:
I am really interested in working with marine mammals. My favorite marine mammal is a whale! So, ask me about whales! I took a course at the University of New Hampshire on marine invertebrates and can ID most New England marine invertebrates.



I want to work with marine animals
I would love to work in an Aquarium post grad




I am currently a senior at the University of New Hampshire studying Zoology with a minor in Marine Biology.



I have lab experience
Thanks for checking out my web site!
